{"tid":1861843,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支那賤畜：「我有點搞不懂做這種研究是為了幹嘛？毀滅人類嗎？」","createTime":"2020-02-04T10:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T11:35:39.000Z","uid":242537,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d94b006aa8bd8099e7c5c42dcc173a007d765066","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:19:11.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎疫情不斷延燒，規模有持續擴大的趨勢，外界將矛頭指向武漢「P4病毒實驗室」，認為病毒可能是從該處流出，但武漢病毒所研究員石正麗以性命擔保極力否認，卻被發現過去曾研發變種冠狀病毒，能有效感染人類呼吸道。<br />\n<br />\n石正麗日前透過通訊APP微信，使用「朋友圈」功能發文指出，「2019新型冠狀病毒是大自然給人類不文明生活習慣的懲罰，我石正麗用我的生命擔保，和實驗室沒有關係，奉勸那些相信並傳播不良媒體的謠言的人」要「閉上你們的臭嘴」。<br />\n<br />\n但石正麗卻被中國網友揭露，2015年曾於國際期刊《自然》（nature）發表1篇名為「1種類似於SARS的循環性蝙蝠冠狀病毒，展現在人體出現的潛力（A SARS-like cluster of circulating bat coronaviruses shows potential for human emergence，暫譯）」研究，研究團隊透過病毒基因重組技術，將中國馬蹄蝠身上的病毒、和小老鼠的Sars病毒重組，產生的新病毒得以與人體的血管收縮素轉化酶2（ACE2）結合，能有效感染人類呼吸道細胞，毒性相當巨大。<br />\n<br />\n該份研究在當時就引發學界不安，《自然》期刊報導指出，其他病毒學家質疑這項研究的必要性，認為這種實驗很難證明任何事情，且還蘊含極大風險，巴黎巴斯德研究所的病毒學家西蒙．韋恩．霍布森（Simon Wain-Hobson）指出，研究人員創造了1種新型病毒，該病毒在人細胞中生長良好，「如果病毒逃脫了，沒有人能夠預測其發展軌跡。」<br />\n<br />\n中國網友得知石正麗的這段往事，儘管目前尚無證據證明武漢肺炎疫情與她有直接關係，仍留言砲轟「中國科研界的底線到底在哪裡，遮羞布都沒有，這麼明目張膽？」、「我有點搞不懂做這種研究是為了幹嘛？毀滅人類嗎」、「她的話還能信嗎？」、「研究這種有什麼意義？她腦子有泡嗎？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3056601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3056601&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=98140389\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3056601&h=ac8ae194\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3056601</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://m1.aboluowang.com/uploadfile/2020/0204/20200204015634107.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm1.aboluowang.com%2Fuploadfile%2F2020%2F0204%2F20200204015634107.png&h=b41942cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/02/A12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2FA12.jpg&h=77f6fca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jOCGFy0sA00/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjOCGFy0sA00%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=ec2ed17a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5599d7ee3abcbb24f050e7d2840b7a814dc59ee6","tid":1861843,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"....2019新型冠狀病毒是大自然給人類不文明生活習慣的懲罰....<br />\n<br />\n某程度上呢句又岩wor"},{"pid":"b483cdf30084f2b92b0610714e714bd7a00d9305","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/elFyFKK_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FelFyFKK_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=5011b960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40bd96822f3b262d226a2cbc63b96ba47b45326b","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4hpiMPq_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4hpiMPq_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=ce2ff6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50be7fddda5f3b50fd890e0e42d5b264c2e6dbc0","tid":1861843,"uid":170335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"由毀滅人類（中国人除外） 變左毀滅中国人"},{"pid":"2d37f554415430d187ef44fc0d0026fd0a493a2d","tid":1861843,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40bd96822f3b262d226a2cbc63b96ba47b45326b","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:24:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4hpiMPq_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4hpiMPq_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dmedium&h=ce2ff6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"有冇link"},{"pid":"a3a3e5db648304e473e3e238f11903ce927f650d","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"《武漢新型肺炎事件病毒來源的三種可能性》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.creaders.net/education/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=1451671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.creaders.net%2Feducation%2Fbbsviewer.php%3Ftrd_id%3D1451671&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=c4597cb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.creaders.net/education/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=1451671</a>"},{"pid":"3e1236eeb1a616829b1cde129a103586bb10d796","tid":1861843,"uid":300474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b69dc212af145f9e001d196b9837475d12b725bc","tid":1861843,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a375d94b0610a0672d95482792811d1888b226","tid":1861843,"uid":121989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:30:20.000Z","msg":"其實佢驚過你地<br />\n俾美國揾到 蛛絲馬跡<br />\n即時變condom"},{"pid":"be2cfc8f8b9e8dbbb3d031de82fa684102e96bc1","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:32:04.000Z","msg":"唔係研究化武 邊個信？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n石正麗研究員1987年7月畢業於武漢大學生物系遺傳專業，獲學士學位。1990年7月畢業於中科院武漢病毒所，獲碩士學位。2000年5月獲法國蒙彼利埃（Montpellier）第二大學博士學位。長期從事新發病毒的研究，在病毒的分離和鑑定、病毒的遺傳進化、病毒的檢測技術、病毒的分子流行病學等方面有長期的積累和研究經驗。<br />\n<br />\n主要貢獻有：在蝙蝠體內發現遺傳多樣的SARS樣冠狀病毒，並首次成功分離到與SARS病毒高度同源的蝙蝠冠狀病毒，證明蝙蝠是SARS冠狀病毒的自然宿主，揭示了SARS病毒從蝙蝠到人的生態傳播鏈(Science, 2005; Nature, 2013)；在我國蝙蝠體內檢測到烈性病毒尼帕病毒和埃博拉病毒的抗體，為蝙蝠病毒引起的烈性新發傳染病的預防提供了預警策略(Emerging Infectious Disease , 2008; Virology Journal, 2012)；首次解析了2種蝙蝠的基因組序列，提示蝙蝠具有獨特的抗病毒免疫特徵，為後續研究蝙蝠抗病毒免疫機制提供了基礎(Science , 2013)；在蝙蝠體內檢測到遺傳多樣的腺病毒、腺相關病毒和圓環病毒，進一步證實蝙蝠是多種病毒的自然宿主（Journal of Virology, 2010; Journal of General Virology, 2010和2011）。"},{"pid":"eac8376e082b49bf62e84e7d0722facf1c36f695","tid":1861843,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50be7fddda5f3b50fd890e0e42d5b264c2e6dbc0","tid":1861843,"uid":170335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"由毀滅人類（中国人除外） 變左毀滅中国人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/07/wFK4H0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2FwFK4H0.png&h=34f10f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqXb0P.gif&h=31e53dd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eacde3b50efeb82542f1c069c223252a94103fac","tid":1861843,"uid":53411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a3e5db648304e473e3e238f11903ce927f650d","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"《武漢新型肺炎事件病毒來源的三種可能性》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.creaders.net/education/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=1451671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.creaders.net%2Feducation%2Fbbsviewer.php%3Ftrd_id%3D1451671&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=c4597cb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.creaders.net/education/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=1451671</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:37:21.000Z","msg":"生物化學武器<br />\n人工改造後的病毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0995b269a3c67e338ab7e27ac14227a6f0814f","tid":1861843,"uid":106477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"有無bio人可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n即係正常嚟講 蝙蝠嘅病毒係傳唔到人？<br />\n要基因改造過先可以？"},{"pid":"d0c07a54b227ff228e5c574d4a4b7857e4908762","tid":1861843,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b0995b269a3c67e338ab7e27ac14227a6f0814f","tid":1861843,"uid":106477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"有無bio人可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n即係正常嚟講 蝙蝠嘅病毒係傳唔到人？<br />\n要基因改造過先可以？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"簡單咁講，病毒需要宿主，而唔係所有宿主都適合果種病毒。病毒可以透過變異去感染新宿主，而變異可以天然或者人工。"},{"pid":"3c58208ec060104fb6115daf71caf4d32a3302bc","tid":1861843,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/28/science/bats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2Fscience%2Fbats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=406adac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/28/science/bats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html</a><br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠係好多病毒嘅宿主，而佢哋嘅免疫系統，已變化到對病毒唔一定會產生反應<br />\n<br />\n最詭異嘅係，大陸嘅研究人員，上年年頭已經發表報告，預言&quot;附於蝙蝠身上嘅病毒，會喺大陸造成大規模嘅感染&quot;"},{"pid":"21507e14a79191d6752b15f8e2b94316149e2753","tid":1861843,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c58208ec060104fb6115daf71caf4d32a3302bc","tid":1861843,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:18:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/28/science/bats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F01%2F28%2Fscience%2Fbats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=406adac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/28/science/bats-coronavirus-Wuhan.html</a><br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠係好多病毒嘅宿主，而佢哋嘅免疫系統，已變化到對病毒唔一定會產生反應<br />\n<br />\n最詭異嘅係，大陸嘅研究人員，上年年頭已經發表報告，預言&quot;附於蝙蝠身上嘅病毒，會喺大陸造成大規模嘅感染&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"係 好撚恐怖<br />\n垃圾國家黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8ecde2dfc98aedb5aa1b22636d298edfdba219","tid":1861843,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T11:35:39.000Z","msg":"妄想 統治世界 之心不死！！"}]}